people, and now put them in a car.

57
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:44,310
What do you know about that?

58
00:03:44,310 --> 00:03:46,672
Only one person can drive.

59
00:03:46,672 --> 00:03:48,713
So if you're critical or

60
00:03:48,713 --> 00:03:55,240
focused brain is driving your diffused
brain is asleep in the back seat.

61
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:58,350
And that's not what anyone
wants when they're writing.

62
00:03:58,350 --> 00:04:01,630
