map on the first day of school.

100
00:06:21,810 --> 00:06:24,640
I wrote the mind map about
the first day of school.

101
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:29,040
So what I wrote in the center of
the page was first day of school.

102
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:32,290
And part of the reason I picked
this topic was because it

103
00:06:32,290 --> 00:06:37,410
