obvious marking points.

104
00:06:37,410 --> 00:06:41,940
So one is grade one,
one is high school, one is university.

105
00:06:41,940 --> 00:06:45,970
So you can have different first days
of school tied to those events.

106
00:06:45,970 --> 00:06:48,270
So then I wrote those down and

107
00:06:48,270 --> 00:06:50,820
you'll see I've marked them
with little cross hatches.

108
00:06:50,820 --> 00:06:52,710
I did that after the fact just so

109
00:06:52,710 --> 00:06:56,140
