114
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:17,330
Well, when I went to grade one,
first day of school I'm standing

115
00:07:17,330 --> 00:07:23,170
in the school yard with my mother and
I got stung on the lip by a bee.

116
00:07:23,170 --> 00:07:26,420
I will never ever forget that moment.

117
00:07:26,420 --> 00:07:31,450
For me first day of school will
always be linked with being stung by

118
00:07:31,450 --> 00:07:33,730
a bee right there on the lip.

119
00:07:33,730 --> 00:07:36,630
So all I have to write is two words,
bee sting.

120
00:07:36,630 --> 00:07:38,480
And everything comes back to me.

121
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:44,410
I can picture the spot, the exact spot
