deal about because I was crying.

124
00:07:52,115 --> 00:07:53,160
You know, so

125
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:59,870
its almost like a movie I can play in my
own brain just based on those two words.

126
00:07:59,870 --> 00:08:04,660
Now one of the questions I often get when
