140
00:08:52,910 --> 00:08:56,580
It's more likely you're going to
be reading a bunch of books, but

141
00:08:56,580 --> 00:08:58,800
the same principle applies.

142
00:08:58,800 --> 00:09:03,960
If there is something that is really
interesting to you and important and

143
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:07,970
integral to your research,
you're likely to remember that.

144
00:09:07,970 --> 00:09:11,330
And the things that are most important
are going to float to the top of

145
00:09:11,330 --> 00:09:12,290
your memory.

146
00:09:12,290 --> 00:09:15,630
So you will remember them and
then you can mind map about them.

147
00:09:16,750 --> 00:09:22,380
>> Well, this is very interesting because
